metadata.title: Palmrest Decal Sticker (2-Pack) + Keyboard Protector Cover Skin for 13.3'' Dell Inspiron 13 7000 Series (Model 13-7378,13-7368, Black Carbon Fiber palmrest Sticker+Black Keyboard Skin)
features: Attention: please check your model including suffix from the label on Dell original package box before buying
